title: Eddie’s Coronavirus Results + Best Duets Draft + Lunchbox Drive-Thru Confessions
itunes:title: Eddie’s Coronavirus Results + Best Duets Draft + Lunchbox Drive-Thru Confessions
description:
We finally get the results of Eddie’s Coronavirus test. Will he walk into the studio or reveal he’s still at home in bed? We draft our favorite duets. Plus, Lunchbox goes to the drive-thru to confess things to employees with hopes they can offer him some advice!
